            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " so public estimates match budget deductions."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Standard norms (ord in {None, 0, 1, 2, inf, -inf}) cost 2*numel FLOPs\n(FMA=2: one multiply + accumulate per element).\nGeneral-p norms cost 18*numel + 16 FLOPs per group: abs(1) + pow(16)\nper element + sum-reduce(1) + final root pow(16). The wrapper's\nn_groups multiplier scales the +16 correctly per group."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
